import React from 'react';

import streamThumbnail from '../../images/stream_thumbnail.jpg';
import {
   List, 
   StreamContainer, 
   StreamRow, 
   StreamThumbnail, 
   StreamColumn, 
   StreamHeader, 
   StreamAvatar,
   StreamUsername, 
   StreamDescription, 
   StreamCategory, 
   TagRow, 
   TagView, 
   TagText } from './styles';

const StreamList: React.FC = () => {
  const StreamItem = () =>(
    <StreamContainer>
      <StreamThumbnail source={streamThumbnail}/>

      <StreamColumn>
        <StreamRow>
          <StreamHeader>
            <StreamAvatar />
            <StreamUsername numberOfLines={1}>Jonathan Andrade</StreamUsername>
          </StreamHeader>

          <StreamDescription numberOfLines={1}>
            Front-end com Next.js, Chakra UI e GraphQL
          </StreamDescription>
          
          <StreamCategory numberOfLines={1}>
            Science & Technology
          </StreamCategory>
          
        </StreamRow>
        
        <TagRow>
          <TagView>
            <TagText>
              Portuguese
            </TagText>
          </TagView>
          <TagView>
            <TagText>
              Web Development
            </TagText>
          </TagView>
        </TagRow>
      </StreamColumn>
    </StreamContainer>
  )

  return (
    <List>
      <StreamItem/>
      <StreamItem/>
      <StreamItem/>
      <StreamItem/>
      <StreamItem/>
      <StreamItem/>
    </List>
  );
};

export default StreamList;
